<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Easy Ways to Check Your Electricity Bill Online</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
    background:#f4f7fb;
    color:#1f2937;
    line-height:1.8;
}

header{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#3b82f6);
    padding:80px 20px;
    color:white;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
}

header::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    width:300px;
    height:300px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius:50%;
    top:-100px;
    right:-80px;
}

.container{
    max-width:1100px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:0 20px;
}

.hero-content{
    position:relative;
    z-index:2;
}

.badge{
    display:inline-block;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    padding:8px 16px;
    border-radius:50px;
    font-size:14px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
}

h1{
    font-size:48px;
    line-height:1.2;
    max-width:750px;
    font-weight:800;
}

.hero-text{
    margin-top:20px;
    max-width:650px;
    font-size:18px;
    opacity:0.95;
}

.main{
    margin-top:-50px;
    position:relative;
    z-index:10;
}

.article-card{
    background:white;
    border-radius:24px;
    padding:50px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

h2{
    margin-top:40px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    font-size:28px;
    color:#111827;
}

p{
    margin-bottom:20px;
    font-size:17px;
    color:#374151;
}

.feature-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
    margin:35px 0;
}

.feature-box{
    background:#f9fbff;
    border:1px solid #e5edf8;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:18px;
    transition:0.3s ease;
}

.feature-box:hover{
    transform:translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
}

.feature-box h3{
    font-size:18px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.cta-box{
    margin-top:40px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eff6ff,#dbeafe);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:40px;
    text-align:center;
}

.cta-box h3{
    font-size:30px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.cta-box p{
    max-width:650px;
    margin:auto;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    padding:14px 28px;
    background:#2563eb;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:12px;
    font-weight:600;
    transition:0.3s ease;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#1d4ed8;
    transform:translateY(-2px);
}

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px 20px;
    color:#6b7280;
    font-size:14px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

    h1{
        font-size:34px;
    }

    .article-card{
        padding:30px 22px;
    }

    .cta-box{
        padding:30px 20px;
    }

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <div class="container hero-content">

        <div class="badge">
            Smart Online Electricity Services
        </div>

        <h1>Easy Ways to Check Your Electricity Bill Online</h1>

        <p class="hero-text">
            Learn how online electricity bill services help users save time,
            access duplicate bills instantly, and manage payments more efficiently.
        </p>

    </div>
</header>

<section class="main">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="article-card">

            <p>
                Managing electricity bills has become much easier with online services.
                Instead of waiting for paper bills or visiting offices, users can now
                check their electricity bills online within seconds from any device.
            </p>

            <h2>Why Online Bill Checking is Helpful</h2>

            <p>
                Online bill systems provide convenience, speed, and accessibility.
                Users only need a reference number to access duplicate bills,
                due dates, and billing details.
            </p>

            <div class="feature-grid">

                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Instant Access</h3>
                    <p>View duplicate bills anytime without waiting for paper copies.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Mobile Friendly</h3>
                    <p>Check bills easily from smartphones, tablets, or desktop devices.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Time Saving</h3>
                    <p>No need to visit customer service offices for bill information.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Better Management</h3>
                    <p>Track payments and monitor monthly electricity expenses easily.</p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <h2>Modern and User Friendly System</h2>

            <p>
                Most electricity bill websites are designed with simple interfaces so
                users can quickly access information without technical knowledge.
                Responsive layouts make the experience smooth across all devices.
            </p>

            <h2>Benefits for Families and Businesses</h2>

            <p>
                Online bill checking helps households and businesses stay organized,
                avoid late payments, and access important billing information instantly.
                This digital approach improves efficiency and convenience for everyone.
            </p>

            <div class="cta-box">

                <h3>Read More Helpful Guides</h3>

                <p>
                    Explore more articles, updates, and useful electricity bill information
                    through our latest blog posts and online service guides.
                </p>

                <a class="btn" href="https://fescobillonline.com/blog/">
                    Visit Blog
                </a>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    © 2026 FESCO Bill Online • All Rights Reserved
</footer>

</body>
</html>